{"tid":2383712,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登政府：中國軍方相關公司投資禁令延期至5月27日","createTime":"2021-01-28T05:36:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T02:46:57.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"2056508a51965ddce018130d7fff8c28c253889f","tid":2383712,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T05:36:02.000Z","msg":"美財政部延遲實施針對懷疑與中國軍方相關公司投資禁令<br />\n<br />\n美國財政部延遲實施，針對懷疑同中國軍方相關公司的投資禁令。特朗普政府11月推出行政命令，並設定於當地時間今天實行，不過拜登政府推遲措施至5月27日才實施。今次是財政部的外國資產控制辦公室發出「一般許可」，作出延期決定。<br />\n<br />\n現時美國新政府正開始審查特朗普針對中國採取的行動，包括特朗普政府把一些中國公司列入國防部和商務部的黑名單，禁止美國人投資這些公司，出口技術予這些公司亦會變得困難。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2376777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2376777&d=LvSu6Mc%2FVB7R449T953cUy3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=05016fa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2376777</a>"},{"pid":"e0ea47183c86d4f089f17830742508679f7f5958","tid":2383712,"uid":64191,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T05:37:18.000Z","msg":"美共無限期延期<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae40461f13a3de9d7c22e3e674e4ba582fe9b664","tid":2383712,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T05:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23cb96adfb0ee3e4acfc5cb5efbdd6d3a238212c","tid":2383712,"uid":256837,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:46:38.000Z","msg":"國際跣：相信拜登"},{"pid":"a0011b52aa0855da05e24258a032b4454769b170","tid":2383712,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0ea47183c86d4f089f17830742508679f7f5958","tid":2383712,"uid":64191,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T05:37:18.000Z"